  <rte>
    <name>A shorter Kentmere Horseshoe</name>
    <desc>The Kentmere Horseshoe is one of the great Lake District high level walks and includes a large number of Wainwrights. This route is a shorter version and includes only the first three summits before returning along the valley to the start.</desc>
	<author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1320-description</url>
